Peronospora on Papaver, which has the important phytopathological implication that wild Papaver spp. cannot play any role as primary inoculum source for downy mildew epidemics in cultivated opium poppy crops.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Voglmayr, Hermann", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Montes-Borrego, Miguel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Landa, Blanca B.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 2", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Species Assessment AIS", "invasive species"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/8ae7dc2478f95dc5b5b0e8ebc9dabe96", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/715afcd687e26848b9ea140637fa35f2d70d2b490ab6f1bd0de6b2a18770dc17", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/2352922/items/D46M5YWN", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/2352922/items/D46M5YWN", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/f8b38165a396640d371b16a6fe106f42!/b26416-28664", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/359bd494433933b868f85e88d3437f76", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.1371/journal.pone.0096838", "relation": "isVariantFormOf", "resource_type": "publication", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.7430682", "relation": "isCitedBy", "resource_type": "publication-report", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "5", "pages": "e96838", "title": "PLoS ONE", "volume": "9"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/8ae7dc2478f95dc5b5b0e8ebc9dabe96"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:2352922:items:D46M5YWN"}, 